The Sack of presents is a cosmetic reward obtained from the 2016 Christmas event, as well as subsequent Christmas events, worn on the cape slot. If destroyed, players can obtain a replacement from Diango in Draynor Village. It provides no bonuses.

This item can be stored in the toy box of a costume room.
